<br>
&quot;SISTERS! BROTHERS! I'm .... i'm *gulps* getting MAWWRIED!!!!!!&quot;<br>
<br>
She skips around the room unable to calm herself.<br>
<br>
&quot;Me! Eviah, I'm getting mawwried, I'm GETTING MAWWRIED!!&quot;<br>
<br>
She stops in the middle and thrusts out her finger, showing a beautiful Rose Platinum Engagement Ring!  The gem is shaded a delicated light pink and the band is made of pure platinum and it fits her finger perfectly.<br>
<br>
She has a fevered look in her eyes, excitement and the adrenaline of the proposal makes her alive and radiant.<br>
<br>
The day June 12, 3180 will be marked forever in her memory.  That is the day that Wardenn Wildrunner asked her to be his wife.<br>
<br>
She opens her journal, the one Mirabor gave her long time ago, and starts to write furiously, trying to calm herself down.<br>
<br>
***************************************************<br>
<br>
12-6-3180<br>
<br>
Today I was asked to be married....<br>
<br>
<br>
***************************************************<br>
<br>
<br>
( ooc:  he asked!!! in the most perfect, absolutely beautiful, thrilling way possible.  It was the right moment and check the Brother's board! )<br>
